  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Corporate secretarial assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist with <strong>ACRA Annual Returns</strong> and <strong>IRAS Corporate Tax Filing</strong></li>\n  <li>Handle <strong>company registration, business license  applications, and director/shareholder changes</strong></li>\n  <li>Prepare financial statements, bookkeeping, and document filing</li>\n  <li>Learn and independently manage daily tasks,proactively solve problems</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or degree in <strong>Accounting or Finance</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>1–2 years of relevant working experience preferred; strong fresh graduates will also be considered</strong></li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented, responsible, with good time management skills</li>\n  <li><strong>Proficient in both English and Chinese (written and spoken)</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong learning ability and problem-solving skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Preferred Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Familiar with <strong>ACRA BizFile+ / IRAS myTax Portal</strong></li>\n  <li>Experience with <strong>Xero, Odoo, or other accounting software</strong></li>\n  <li>Relevant internship or project experience</li>\n  <li>Committed to long-term development in corporate services or accounting</li>\n</ul>",
